## ðŸš€ Development Workflow

### Before Starting Work

1. **Read Documentation**:
   ```
   - Read: AGENT_REFERENCE_GUIDE.md (relevant sections)
   - Check: Common Pitfalls (section 12)
   - Review: Pre-Flight Checklist (section 15)
