## ðŸŽ¨ Code Style Standards

### TypeScript
- Use explicit types (no `any` unless absolutely necessary)
- Prefer `async/await` over promises
- Use optional chaining: `obj?.prop ?? default`

### React Components
- Functional components only
- Hooks at top of function
- Effects after functions

### Naming
- Files: `kebab-case.tsx`
- Components: `PascalCase`
- Functions: `camelCase`
- Constants: `UPPER_SNAKE_CASE`
- Database: `snake_case`

### File Organization
```
/app/api/          â†’ API routes
/app/components/   â†’ React components
/lib/              â†’ Business logic
/db/               â†’ Database (schema, migrations)
/prompts/          â†’ AI prompts
/__tests__/        â†’ Unit tests
/e2e/              â†’ E2E tests
```

